{"markdown":"[![Stamp, the AI Secretary that handles your email and calendar for you.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-full-950.8388102a.svg)](https://www.stampmail.ai/)\n\n- [Features](https://www.stampmail.ai/features)\n- [Pricing](https://www.stampmail.ai/pricing)\n- [Contact](mailto:sales@stampmail.ai)\n- [Sign In](https://www.stampmail.ai/auth)\n- [Get Started](https://www.stampmail.ai/auth)\n\nFeatures Designed for Doers.\n\nExplore the features that enable Stamp to handle your emails for you.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F01.4d3116c4.png&w=640&q=75)![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F03.23c32929.png&w=640&q=75)![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F04.abde93b3.png&w=640&q=75)![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2F02.9ad85271.png&w=640&q=75)\n\nInbox On Autopilot\n\nStamp Mode: Just Press Enter\n\nStamp automatically drafts replies, prioritizes, and categorizes emails. Enter Stamp Mode and blaze through your inbox by simply approving Stamp's changes.\n\n![Automatic Replies. Stamp automatically drafts replies to emails when you receive them, using memories and related context to produce replies that sound exactly like you.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fauto_replies.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nAutomatic Replies\n\nStamp automatically drafts replies to emails when you receive them, using memories and related context to produce replies that sound exactly like you.\n\n![Automatic Labels. Stamp applies labels to all emails you receive based on your plain english descriptions.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fauto_categories.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nAutomatic Labels\n\nStamp applies labels to all emails you receive based on your plain english descriptions.\n\n![Summaries & Todos. Stamp automatically generates summaries for important emails and extracts todos so you never forget to follow up.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Ftodos.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nSummaries & Todos\n\nStamp automatically generates summaries for important emails and extracts todos so you never forget to follow up.\n\nYour Personal Secretary\n\nAgentic Chat & Composer\n\nStamp's Agents perform any task you delegate to them, intelligently gathering context to produce a tailored result every time.\n\n![Bulk Draft Replies. Stamp's Agent can draft multiple replies with a single prompt.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fagent_bulk_draft.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nBulk Draft Replies\n\nStamp's Agent can draft multiple replies with a single prompt.\n\n![Gathers Context. Stamp's Agent and Composer search through your contacts and past emails to automatically populate recipient emails and generate personalized drafts.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fagentic_composer.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nGathers Context\n\nStamp's Agent and Composer search through your contacts and past emails to automatically populate recipient emails and generate personalized drafts.\n\n![Search the Web. Stamp's Agent and Composer can search the web for additional context to incorporate into your conversation or drafts.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fagent_web_search.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nSearch the Web\n\nStamp's Agent and Composer can search the web for additional context to incorporate into your conversation or drafts.\n\n![Send Calendar Invites. Stamp's Agent can create or modify events on your calendar.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fagent_calendar.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nSend Calendar Invites\n\nStamp's Agent can create or modify events on your calendar.\n\n![Email Citations. Stamp's Agent extracts information from your emails to answer your questions and provides citations for the emails it used.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fagent_citations.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nEmail Citations\n\nStamp's Agent extracts information from your emails to answer your questions and provides citations for the emails it used.\n\n![Performs Any Action. Stamp's Agent can perform any action in your inbox, such as trashing emails, archiving emails, or categorizing emails.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fagent_trash.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nPerforms Any Action\n\nStamp's Agent can perform any action in your inbox, such as trashing emails, archiving emails, or categorizing emails.\n\nFilter Out The Noise\n\nIntelligent Labelling\n\nCreate custom labels with plain english descriptions to automatically categorize and triage incoming emails.\n\n![Label Actions. Specify what actions to to perform on emails in a particular label, and Stamp will perform them for you.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Flabel_actions.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nLabel Actions\n\nSpecify what actions to to perform on emails in a particular label, and Stamp will perform them for you.\n\n![Priority Inbox. Stamp's priority inbox ensures important emails are always at the top of your inbox.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fauto_prioritize.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nPriority Inbox\n\nStamp's priority inbox ensures important emails are always at the top of your inbox.\n\n![Long Term Memories. Stamp uses long term term memories you've provided to automatically personalize replies, categorization, and todos.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2Ffeatures%2Fmemories.png&w=1920&q=75)\n\nLong Term Memories\n\nStamp uses long term term memories you've provided to automatically personalize replies, categorization, and todos.\n\nReady To Transform Your Email?\n\nTry Stamp for 30 days free. Experience what it's like to take control of your inbox and your day.\n\n[Get Started Today](https://www.stampmail.ai/auth)![Get started with Stamp today.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Finbox.3ca53269.png&w=2048&q=75)\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nRe: Project Proposal\n\nHarold reached out regarding specifics on your upcoming presentation.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nRe: Pull Request\n\nRobert replied to your pull request suggestion with an alternate approach.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nRe: Setting Up Stamp\n\nGeorge reached out to inquire about setting up Stamp for his team of 15 people.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nWelcome to Stamp!\n\nArchit reached out personally to welcome you to Stamp and highlight key features.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nNew Stamp Features\n\nThe Stamp team highlighted new features coming to Stamp that will further improve Stamp's email handling capabilities.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nRe: Scheduling Product Sync\n\nSteve sent across the agenda for the upcoming product sync and confirmed his availability.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nImpressed With Stamp\n\nJames is highly impressed with Stamp's AI Secretary capabilities and proposed several potential new features.\n\n![](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-partial-blue.6fc6f02a.svg)\n\nAnalytics Overview\n\nYou received a product analytics overview for your website, highlighting strong user growth and retention.\n\n![Stamp, The AI Secretary that handles your email and calendar for you.](https://www.stampmail.ai/_next/static/media/stamp-full-blue.fe9a54e1.svg)\n\nPages\n\n[Home](https://www.stampmail.ai/) [Features](https://www.stampmail.ai/features) [Pricing](https://www.stampmail.ai/pricing) [Sign Up](https://www.stampmail.ai/auth)\n\nCompany\n\n[Careers](https://www.workatastartup.com/companies/stamp) [Contact Us](mailto:sales@stampmail.ai)\n\nData\n\n[Privacy Policy](https://www.stampmail.ai/privacy) [Terms of Service](https://www.stampmail.ai/tos)\n\nMedia\n\n[LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/company/stamp-ai/) [X / Twitter](https://x.com/StampMail) [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/@StampMail)\n\n© 2026 Stamp AI\n\nPrivacy Policy\n\nTerms of Service","metadata":{"description":"The AI Secretary that handles your email and calendar for you.","title":"Stamp","language":"en","viewport":"width=device-width, initial-scale=1","favicon":"https://www.stampmail.ai/icon.ico?7316892dfd296030","scrapeId":"019d3498-60e3-74cc-a8f1-6ca17c784259","sourceURL":"https://www.stampmail.ai/features","url":"https://www.stampmail.ai/features","statusCode":200,"contentType":"text/html; charset=utf-8","proxyUsed":"basic","cacheState":"hit","cachedAt":"2026-03-27T08:51:08.785Z","creditsUsed":1,"concurrencyLimited":false},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" data-sentry-component=\"RootLayout\" data-sentry-source-file=\"layout.tsx\"><body class=\"__variable_16e121 __variable_e10f34 __variable_47a102 bg-neutral-50\"><main><div class=\"h-screen w-screen bg-white flex flex-col items-center overflow-x-clip overflow-y-auto\" data-sentry-component=\"Features\" data-sentry-source-file=\"features.tsx\"><div class=\"max-w-[1512px] relative\"><nav data-sentry-element=\"Navbar\" data-sentry-component=\"HomeNav\" data-sentry-source-file=\"homeNav.tsx\" class=\"flex h-auto items-center justify-center data-[menu-open=true]:border-none top-0 inset-x-0 backdrop-blur-lg data-[menu-open=true]:backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-150 fixed bg-transparent shadow-none z-[999] p-[5px] w-full transition-all duration-200\" style=\"--navbar-height:4rem\"><header class=\"z-40 flex px-6 gap-4 w-full flex-row relative flex-nowrap items-center justify-between h-[var(--navbar-height)] max-w-[1024px]\"><ul class=\"flex gap-4 h-full flex-row flex-nowrap items-center data-[justify=start]:justify-start